data.description: Amazing 4 bedroom, 2/5 bath executive home on large corner lot in cul-du-sac, with two-car side entry garage. You are welcomed by custom iron estate double doors, and an open foyer. Entertain your guest in formal living, dining, large family or custom paved patio in yard. The amply sized master has huge attached study joined by French doors for a private retreat. The additional 3 bedrooms are each nicely sized providing room to grow or to have extra rooms to be used as office or exercise rooms. Seller downsizing and this home is awaiting the perfect family. $6,000 Any Way You want, can be applied towards Buyer's cosmetic repairs or closing costs.
